---
import "./ExecutionIsolationRow.css";
---

<div class="execution-isolation-copy">
    <h2>Absolute Execution Isolation</h2>
    <p>
        Hyper-threading is disabled on all our compute. Every workload runs
        inside a hardened microVM. Dedicated reservations add physical core
        assignment and CPU pinning for workloads that need more predictable
        execution.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="execution-isolation-visual" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
        class="execution-isolation-visual__asset"
        src="/assets/product/execution-isolation.svg"
        alt=""
    />
</div>
